{"tid":1326071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜長太美 女職員邊工作邊偷看","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:56:31.000Z","uid":1086,"like":20,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"eab9bad275811ee0fac1dbe21473ead44446f561","tid":1326071,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE昨（15日）出發LA展開巡迴演唱會，成員子瑜在進入出境大廳時，一張機場女員工因為她太漂亮，檢查完護照後的驚訝表情全被拍下，於網路掀起熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE成員除了休養中的Mina，昨8成員現身仁川機場，準備出發前往LA展開巡迴演唱會，而幫子瑜檢查完護照的女員工，邊工作邊盯著她的臉，直到子瑜離開後，才立刻轉頭發出「哇」的讚嘆聲，似乎是被對方美貌嚇到，真實反應笑壞網友。<br />\n<br />\n子瑜已連兩年登上「TC Candler」全球百大美女榜單，前年獲得全國第三美，去年則前進一個名次拿下亞軍，成為世界第二、亞洲第一美，而在2018年的「亞太區百大美女排行榜」中，也獲得第四名的成績，美貌不容小覷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/C65eWXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FC65eWXq.jpg&h=0a36e451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機場女職員看到子瑜被美貌嚇到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A6H4NQaPFSo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA6H4NQaPFSo&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aueoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=422ef9e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A6H4NQaPFSo</a>"},{"pid":"3153dbecb80da0e6b33dd36124996a6d15d72d3e","tid":1326071,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"牙魚超靚"},{"pid":"e21c20b1998188b7e1a5e7bca86a375f4e1da989","tid":1326071,"uid":1086,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/07/16/190716-10916-2-UjyGb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2F190716-10916-2-UjyGb.jpg&h=fe5339d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f53863fe4c62d92bb54201a97bb78b8d424422fa","tid":1326071,"uid":1086,"like":5,"dislike":22,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2019/07/16/190716-10916-6-pmd1V.jpg\" 